casebody.data:
Clarence P. Bilhorn et al., Appellants, v William G. Farlow, Jr., et al., Respondents. Submitted January 17, 1977; decided February 24, 1977

Reported below, 54 AD2d 1120.

Motion to dismiss the appeal herein granted and the appeal dismissed, with costs and $20 costs of motion to respondent Smithkline Corporation, upon the ground that the order appealed from involves the exercise of discretion of a type not reviewable by the Court of Appeals.
